15/10/2003
ZAGREB, Croatia -- President Stipe Mesic met on Tuesday (14 October) with BiH presidency chairman and Croat member Dragan Covic, and discussed ways to resolve pending issues.
Covic was in Zagreb for the opening of the exhibition "Old Bridge in Mostar -- Symbol of Peace".
After their meeting, Mesic said they discussed the bilateral agreement on the Ploce port and construction of the Corridor Vc transport corridor.
They also discussed the possibility of nationals crossing the interstate border using identity cards only.
(BiH Federation TV, HINA, BBC, Mina - 14/10/03)
